    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. Saag Masala is a spinach-based curry, flavoured with garam masala, ground fenugreek and sliced garlic. You'll serve it with buttered pilau rice spiced with aromatic cardamom for a tasty take on a takeaway favourite!",
